    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for any driver. The engine runs smoothly with no known issues, and the transmission shifts cleanly through all gears. While the interior and exterior show some light signs of use typical for its age, there are no major cosmetic flaws or mechanical concerns. You can expect a dependable driving experience with all major systems functioning as intended.",
